If you've ever had an idea to make money, Dragons' Den is THE show to watch.
All manner of money-spinning minds will step into the intimidating world of
business financing, determined to make their dreams come true. All they need is
the cash. To get this, they must face the Dragons, all of whom are formidable
business thinkers with the money to make things happen.
 
 But this is no lottery - the contestants will need all their powers of
reasoning, presentation and persuasion to convince our five business experts
that theirs is a product worth investing in. The Dragons know what makes a
successful idea, how much it's worth and how much cash is needed to get it off

they lose it all.
